## Version 2.1.0

Camera preview rendering enhancements

Changes and fixes:
* Bug fix about preview rotation not being computed correctly
* Build for all supported Android ABI
* Changed the camera exposure to have brighter previews
* Updated the API for better control over preview rendering

Known Issues:
* Camera gets closed and re-opened on screen rotation causing some devices to make a 'click' noise
* Preview gets upside down if the device is quickly rotated to an angle of 180 degrees
